enhanced_by.reason: Both methods handle the addition of values to the Option, with processValue being more detailed in handling separators.
clearValues resets the values list, which can be useful to ensure a clean state before adding new values in tests.
getValues retrieves the list of values added to the Option, which can be used to verify the correctness of the addValue method.
getValue retrieves a specific value from the list, which can be used to verify individual values added by addValue.
